									<h2>Avoiding Extinction</h2>
									<h3>Giving Mexico’s rarest porpoise, the vaquita, a fighting chance in the face of poverty, corruption, and greed.</h3>
									<p class="insidepagethumbinfodate">Sep 20, 2017 | 4,800 words, about 24 minutes</p>
								</header>
