																				<article class="col insidepagethumbholder rotator ">
								<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/features/will-exporting-farmed-totoaba-fix-the-big-mess-pushing-the-worlds-most-endangered-porpoise-to-extinction/" class="tagmanager" id="Related_article_37782" >
								<img width="900" height="432" src="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-totoaba-aquaculture.jpg" class="insidepagethumb wp-post-image" alt="totoaba" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-totoaba-aquaculture.jpg 2500w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-totoaba-aquaculture-520x250.jpg 520w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-totoaba-aquaculture-768x369.jpg 768w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-totoaba-aquaculture-1200x576.jpg 1200w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-totoaba-aquaculture-1536x738.jpg 1536w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-totoaba-aquaculture-2048x984.jpg 2048w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-totoaba-aquaculture-900x432.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" />								<header class="insidepagethumbinfo">
									<h2>Will Exporting Farmed Totoaba Fix the Big Mess Pushing the World’s Most Endangered Porpoise to Extinction?</h2>
									<h3>International officials will soon decide the fate of Mexican totoaba fish farming—and with it, possibly the last glimmer of hope for the vaquita.</h3>
									<p class="insidepagethumbinfodate">Feb 22, 2022 | 1,800 words, about 9 minutes</p>
